    "## Part 11: Semantic Routing\n",
    "\n",
    "语义路由基于查询与预定义提示词之间的语义相似性进行路由决策。\n",
    "\n",
    "### 语义路由的核心概念\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **语义嵌入**: 将查询和候选提示词转换为向量表示\n",
    "2. **相似性计算**: 使用余弦相似度比较语义相似性\n",
    "3. **动态选择**: 选择最相似的提示词模板\n",
    "4. **上下文适应**: 根据查询语义调整回答风格\n",
    "\n",
    "### 与逻辑路由的区别\n",
    "\n",
    "- **逻辑路由**: 基于明确的分类规则\n",
    "- **语义路由**: 基于语义相似性的柔性匹配\n",
    "- **适用场景**: 逻辑路由适合结构化分类，语义路由适合开放式场景"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "semantic_routing_implementation",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 语义路由实现"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "53cbfa72-c35a-4d1d-aa6d-08a570ab2170",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from langchain.utils.math import cosine_similarity\n",
    "from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser\n",
    "from langchain_core.prompts import PromptTemplate\n",
    "from langchain_core.runnables import RunnableLambda, RunnablePassthrough\n",
    "from langchain_openai import ChatOpenAI, OpenAIEmbeddings\n",
    "\n",
    "# 定义两个专业领域的提示词模板\n",
    "# 物理教授模板：专门回答物理学问题\n",
    "physics_template = \"\"\"You are a very smart physics professor. \\\n",
    "You are great at answering questions about physics in a concise and easy to understand manner. \\\n",
    "When you don't know the answer to a question you admit that you don't know.\n",
    "\n",
    "Here is a question:\n",
    "{query}\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# 数学家模板：专门回答数学问题\n",
    "math_template = \"\"\"You are a very good mathematician. You are great at answering math questions. \\\n",
    "You are so good because you are able to break down hard problems into their component parts, \\\n",
    "answer the component parts, and then put them together to answer the broader question.\n",
    "\n",
    "Here is a question:\n",
    "{query}\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# 使用OpenAI嵌入模型计算语义相似性\n",
    "embeddings = OpenAIEmbeddings()\n",
    "prompt_templates = [physics_template, math_template]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 预计算提示词模板的嵌入向量\n",
    "# 提高运行时效率，避免重复计算\n",
    "prompt_embeddings = embeddings.embed_documents(prompt_templates)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 定义语义路由函数\n",
    "def prompt_router(input):\n",
    "    # 嵌入用户查询\n",
    "    query_embedding = embeddings.embed_query(input[\"query\"])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算与预定义模板的余弦相似度\n",
    "    similarity = cosine_similarity([query_embedding], prompt_embeddings)[0]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 选择最相似的模板\n",
    "    most_similar = prompt_templates[similarity.argmax()]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 输出路由决策（用于调试）\n",
    "    print(\"Using MATH\" if most_similar == math_template else \"Using PHYSICS\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 返回选定的提示词模板\n",
    "    return PromptTemplate.from_template(most_similar)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 构建语义路由链\n",
    "# 查询 -> 路由选择 -> LLM -> 输出解析\n",
    "chain = (\n",
    "    {\"query\": RunnablePassthrough()}\n",
    "    | RunnableLambda(prompt_router)\n",
    "    | ChatOpenAI()\n",
    "    | StrOutputParser()\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
